==Further reading==
Discontinued e-book reader software
* The [https://web.archive.org/web/20140625190518/https://readmill.com/epilogue Readmill] app, introduced in February 2011, read numerous formats on Android and [[IOS (operating system)|iOS]] devices but shut down on July 1, 2014.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tuaw.com/2014/06/24/readmill-is-closing-its-doors-on-july-1-2014-needs-picture/?ncid=rss_truncated|date=June 24, 2014| work=The Unofficial Apple Weblog|author= Bond, John-Michael | title=Readmill is closing its doors on July 1, 2014}}</ref>

