{{Infobox Bibliographic Database |title = Current Index to Statistics |image = |caption = |producer = The [[Institute of Mathematical Statistics]] & the [[American Statistical Association]] |country = [[United States|USA]] |history = |languages = [[English language|English]] |providers = Current Index to Statistics |cost = Subscription |disciplines = [[Statistics]] |depth = Index, abstracts |formats = [[Academic journal]] articles, books |temporal = 1975 - present. Limited pre-1975 material. |geospatial = |number = |updates = Annually |p_title = |p_dates = |ISSN = |web = http://www.statindex.org/ |titles = http://www.statindex.org/CIS/ReleaseInfo/info.html }}
The '''Current Index to Statistics''' is an online database published by the [[Institute of Mathematical Statistics]] and the [[American Statistical Association]] that contains bibliographic data of articles in [[statistics]], [[probability]], and related fields.
==See also== * [[Web of Science]] * [[IEEE Xplore]]
==External links== * [http://www.statindex.org Official website]
